S.FORM: Greece Gaga kska Owcow ka Greece, 39 00 N, 22 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 131,957 sq km(hangan na o Tg97)(knlbanga dxgal o 130,647 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 1,310 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 10,773,253 hiyi. Gaga Athens ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 25 idas 3 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Greece ga wada sugan 63.40 ka dxgal qpahan, 30.50 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 6.10 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Prokopis Pavlopoulos, pnaah hngkawas2015 idas 3 jiyax 13pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
